        "description": "### Synopsis\nRetrieve data samples for the specified collector. \n\n### Prerequsites\n\n### Adjusting the Sample Window\nBy default, samples for the last 12 hours are returned. This sample window can be adjusted using query parameters as outlined below.\n\n#### Sample a Fixed Date Range\nThis is how you do it\n\n#### Sample a Relative Date Range\nThis is how you do it",
